[src:aws-x-ray/observability] The rationale for this test is that if n columns are linearly independent, then each of the n state variables is viewable through linear combinations of the output variables y .
[src:aws-x-ray/observability] Observability is a sufficient and necessary condition for the design of continuous-time state observers.
